{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "76ca097e-9f57-4000-a3fe-dfe296ab56a2", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/76ca097e-9f57-4000-a3fe-dfe296ab56a2@1.pkg/1772597601522/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597602712", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/76ca097e-9f57-4000-a3fe-dfe296ab56a2@1.pkg/1772597601522/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597602712"}, "identifier": "76ca097e-9f57-4000-a3fe-dfe296ab56a2", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查人大代表的职权和义务。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>D:对于&ldquo;小区停车问题严重&rdquo;，人大代表可以组织业主、物业、居委会等召开协调会，听取各方意见，协同业主和物业一起协商解决方案，故D说法正确;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>A: 国家机关严厉处罚违停车辆，不是&ldquo;人大代表&rdquo;，说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>B：人大代表应该积极反映和推动解决问题，不应该把责任推卸给物业，说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C:人大代表应该履行协调、监督的职责，而不是把责任直接推卸给物业，说法错误;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）随着城市化持续推进和居民生活水平提升，私家车数量大幅增加，小区停车难题日益突出。车辆挤占道路、绿化带乃至消防通道，对环境美观、居民出行及公共安全造成影响。假如你是人大代表，你会（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）随着城市化持续推进和居民生活水平提升，私家车数量大幅增加，小区停车难题日益突出。车辆挤占道路、绿化带乃至消防通道，对环境美观、居民出行及公共安全造成影响。假如你是人大代表，你会（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/76ca097e-9f57-4000-a3fe-dfe296ab56a2@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755140541085", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对违规停放的车辆进行严厉处罚</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>告知业主向物业索要专属停车位</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>告知业主此事属物业负责，人大代表无权管</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>听取各方意见，协调业主与物业协商解难题</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）随着城市化持续推进和居民生活水平提升，私家车数量大幅增加，小区停车难题日益突出。车辆挤占道路、绿化带乃至消防通道，对环境美观、居民出行及公共安全造成影响。假如你是人大代表，你会（ ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342